</programlisting></para>
<para>where <computeroutput>keyword</computeroutput> is one of: <computeroutput>bdf1</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>bdf2</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>cranknicolson</computeroutput>. </para>
</sect2>
